prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D watercolor illustration for a greeting card front. In the center, a cartoon-style illustration of a young couple, Jordan and Lao Lao, based on the reference photo. Lao Lao, an East Asian woman with long, straight dark brown hair and thin-framed round glasses, is on the left. She is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt and has a happy smile. Jordan, a Southeast Asian man with short, dark, slightly tousled hair, stands behind her, wrapping his arms around her in a loving hug. He is wearing a tan-colored hoodie and has a big, joyful smile. Their clothing should be exactly as in the photo, but with any logos or text removed. The illustration is lighthearted and humorous, with slightly exaggerated happy expressions. The scene is rendered in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds in blues, tans, and greys.

In the center of the card, layered over the illustration, is text in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script that reads: "Happy Birthday to my favorite human!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
